{
  "stem": "26276.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, a lot of those-- I don't know what you call this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But most the military at that time-- the Polish had it too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, they came in on horses, and motorcycles, and trucks, cars.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Anything you want to think of, they came in on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's as soon they took-- yes, they came in and they took over.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, they had to set-- they set up the shop right aways.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they had bigger homes to set up shop.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was not big enough for them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took schools, gymnasium-- there had a lot of those big buildings to take over.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's what they did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just talking about it to ask questions-- what's going to be now?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, at that time, what it was just go on I think like nothing happened.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But a few days later, they came out-- like outside, they had the plaques written on it, you know, that Jews are going to have to wear white arm bands with the Star of David.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And every Jew should come to a certain place to collect the arm bands.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's how it started.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember if I went or my parents went.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I remember that they brought me home one and I wore it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And instead wearing it here, where we did supposed to, I wore it  lower.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I figured if I go someplace, that I don't want to be recognized.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I could closely put it in, my hand into the pocket, and it would hide the band.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, I could bring down a little lower and just put it into the pocket with my hand.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All the time.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, your own home nobody saw you, so you didn't have to.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
